propActive: Sets the step as active. Is passed to child components.
propClasses: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.
propCompleted: Mark the step as completed. Is passed to child components.
propDisabled:
Mark the step as disabled, will also disable the button if
`StepButton` is a child of `Step`. Is passed to child components.
propIndex:
The position of the step.
The prop defaults to the value inherited from the parent Stepper component.
propLast:
If `true`, the Step is displayed as rendered last.
The prop defaults to the value inherited from the parent Stepper component.
stylesRoot: Styles applied to the root element.
stylesHorizontal: Styles applied to the root element if `orientation="horizontal"`.
stylesVertical: Styles applied to the root element if `orientation="vertical"`.
stylesAlternativeLabel: Styles applied to the root element if `alternativeLabel={true}`.
stylesCompleted: Pseudo-class applied to the root element if `completed={true}`.
